    public class LevelOne
extends LevelParent
    The LevelOne class extends LevelParent and is the first level in a series of three. The level focuses on mental health and the effects it has on individuals.

    Course Info:

    ICS4U0 with Krasteva, V.
    Version:
    0.2
    Author:
    Liam Telenko and Russell Leong
